trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **NavigationFailed** event.
trans-unit.target: Disponibiliza dados para o **NavigationFailed** eventos.

trans-unit.source: These event arguments contain information about a navigation that failed, and are passed to handlers of the **NavigationFailed** event, which is implemented by the following: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> NavigationFailedEventArgs encapsulates the following details of the failed navigation request: - **Navigation Initiation**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Estes argumentos de eventos contêm informações sobre uma navegação que falhou e é transmitida para os processadores do **NavigationFailed** evento, o que é implementado pelo seguinte:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>NavigationFailedEventArgs encapsula os seguintes detalhes do pedido de navegação com falhas:- **início de navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Navigator%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Application.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Exception**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navegação exceção**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Handled%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Exception%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Content**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navegação conteúdo**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.Uri%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Details**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Detalhes de navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebResponse%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation State**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navegação estado**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Exception> that was raised as the result of a failed navigation.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref:System.Exception>que foi gerado em resultado de uma navegação falhou.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Exception> will be either a <xref:System.Net.WebException> or an <xref:System.IO.IOException>
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Exception>poderá ser um <xref:System.Net.WebException>ou um <xref:System.IO.IOException></xref:System.IO.IOException> </xref:System.Net.WebException></xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception> that was raised as the result of a failed navigation.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Exception>que foi gerado em resultado de uma navegação falhou.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: Gets the optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation commenced.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os dados opcionais <xref:System.Object>transmitido quando navegação iniciada.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: ExtraData can be used to pass context-specific data that is specific to a particular navigation.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData pode ser utilizado para transmitir dados específicos do contexto que são específicos para uma determinado navegação.

trans-unit.source: ExtraData contains a reference to the object that is passed as the second argument when calling either <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData contém uma referência ao objeto de que é transmitida como segundo argumento ao chamar o <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>ou <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, é `null`.

trans-unit.source: The optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation commenced.
trans-unit.target: Os dados opcionais <xref:System.Object>transmitido quando navegação iniciada.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the failed navigation exception has been handled.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define se a exceção de falha de navegação foi processada.

trans-unit.source: When you handle <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed> to process an exception that is thrown as a result of a failed navigation, and you don't want [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to continue processing the exception, you should set the Handled property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Ao processar <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>para processar uma exceção que é acionada devido a uma falha de navegação e não pretende [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para continuar a processar a excepção, deve definir a propriedade Handled para `true`.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.NavigationFailed>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the exception is handled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> (default).
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se a exceção é processada; caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> (predefinição).

trans-unit.source: The navigator that raised this event.
trans-unit.target: O navegador que originou este evento.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that is the navigator that raised this event
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Object>que seja navegador gerado que este evento</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that could not be navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] para o conteúdo que foi não utilizado.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Uri> for the content that could not be navigated to.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Uri>para o conteúdo que não foi possível ser direcionado para.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: Gets the web request that was used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o pedido web que foi utilizado para pedir o conteúdo especificado.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a web request, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>é uma classe base abstracta que encapsula um pedido web e desconhece o protocolo.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> and extends it with protocol-specific state and behavior, including: - <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: Para cada protocolo comum, o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] inclui uma classe que deriva de <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>e expande-lo com o estado de específicas do protocolo e o comportamento, incluindo:- <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizam o `pack://` esquema para os ficheiros de dados de aplicação de pedido (consulte [WPF recurso de aplicação, o conteúdo e os ficheiros de dados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizam o `http://` esquema para ficheiros de pedidos de servidores Web.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizam o `ftp://` esquema para ficheiros de pedidos de servidores FTP.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizam o `file://` esquema para pedir ficheiros locais.</xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> object that was used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> objeto que foi utilizado para pedir o conteúdo especificado.

trans-unit.source: If navigating to an object, WebRequest is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Se navegar para um objeto, WebRequest é <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the web response that was returned after attempting to download the requested the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a resposta da web que foi devolvida ao tentar transferir o pedido de conteúdo especificado.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a web response, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>é uma classe base abstracta que encapsula uma resposta da web e desconhece o protocolo.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> and extends it with protocol-specific state, including: - <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: Para cada protocolo comum, o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] inclui uma classe que deriva de <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>e expande-lo com o estado de protocolo específico, incluindo:- <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizam o `pack://` esquema para os ficheiros de dados de aplicação de pedido (consulte [WPF recurso de aplicação, o conteúdo e os ficheiros de dados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebResponse> </xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizam o `http://` esquema para ficheiros de pedidos de servidores Web.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizam o `ftp://` esquema para ficheiros de pedidos de servidores FTP.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] que utilizam o `file://` esquema para pedir ficheiros locais.</xref:System.Net.FileWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> that was returned after attempting to download the requested the specified content.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Net.WebResponse?displayProperty=fullName> que foi devolvido ao tentar transferir o pedido de conteúdo especificado.

trans-unit.source: If the navigation failed, WebResponse is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A navegação falhou, WebResponse estiver <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.
